    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-08-12T18:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-08-12T18:00:00-05:00" n="174"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d174">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">860d.51/8–946: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Finland</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hamilton</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">u.s. urgent</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1946-08-12T19:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 12, 1946—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>177. <gloss target="#t_urtel1">Urtel</gloss> 560 Aug. 9. Further credit <gloss
                        target="#t_Eximbank1">Eximbank</gloss> out of question at this time. Visit
                    of Mission to US most undesirable and should be indefinitely postponed. <gloss
                        target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss> and <gloss target="#t_Eximbank1"
                        >Eximbank</gloss> fear reference to private bank financing merely pretext to
                    open discussions with <gloss target="#t_Eximbank1">Eximbank</gloss>. Bank not
                    informed about proposed visit and is not prepared to negotiate.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
